Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:43.72,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.5}Stay the night　傷だらけの夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:52.92,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.5}You save my life　かざした刃の先に想いを重ねた
